1. Gledao sam *spoljašnjost* kuće i primetio da je fasada oštećena. (I was looking at the *exterior* of the house and noticed that the facade was damaged.)
2. Da li si proverio *spoljni* pritisak u gumama pre puta? (Did you check the *external* tire pressure before the trip?)
3. Ne mogu da se setim da li je prozor *spolja* bio zatvoren. (I can't remember if the window was closed *from the outside*.)
4. Koliko je dugo trajao *spoljni* audit u vašoj firmi? (How long did the *external* audit last in your company?)
5. Napolju je bilo jako hladno, pa smo ostali *spolja* samo nekoliko minuta. (It was very cold outside, so we stayed *outside* for only a few minutes.)
6. *Spoljašnji* deo knjige bio je oštećen, ali unutrašnjost je bila u savršenom stanju. (The *outer* part of the book was damaged, but the inside was in perfect condition.)
7. Deca su se igrala *spolja*, dok su roditelji ostali unutra. (The children were playing *outside*, while the parents stayed inside.)
8. Moraćemo da angažujemo *spoljnje* stručnjake za rešavanje ovog problema. (We will need to hire *external* experts to solve this problem.)
9. *Spolja* se nije videlo šta se dešavalo unutra, ali čulo se bučno pevanje. (You couldn't see what was happening *from the outside*, but you could hear loud singing.)
10. Da li si video *spoljašnji* izgled novog hotela u centru grada? (Did you see the *external* appearance of the new hotel in the city center?)